    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Ferny Hills?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Ferny Hills values are driven by block size, the suburb's elevated hilly terrain and leafy established character, and its position between Keperra and Ferny Grove on the outer northern corridor. Larger blocks on elevated positions with bush outlook consistently attract the strongest buyer interest. The Ferny Grove State High School catchment and Ferny Hills State School are active draws for families, and limited supply of large lots within Brisbane city limits supports long-term price resilience.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Ferny Hills?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Ferny Hills homes typically sell within 28 to 42 days. Elevated blocks with bush outlook and north-facing aspects attract faster campaigns than flat street-level lots. Buyers arriving at a Ferny Hills open home have typically shortlisted the suburb already and are focused on the specific property rather than still deciding on location.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Ferny Hills?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Ferny Hills offers a quiet, leafy lifestyle on elevated hilly terrain that delivers genuine space and privacy. Tree-lined streets, large blocks and an established residential character create an environment that feels distinctly different from the inner suburbs while remaining within Brisbane's city boundary. The Keperra and Ferny Grove stations on the Ferny Grove train line give residents practical CBD access, and working-from-home flexibility has made that commute even more manageable for many households.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Ferny Hills a good suburb to sell in right now?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Ferny Hills has maintained consistent demand from families seeking large blocks and an elevated, leafy setting within Brisbane's boundary. Buyers priced out of Keperra regularly extend their search to Ferny Hills, providing a steady motivated buyer pool. The suburb's hilly character and genuinely large lot sizes are scarce within Brisbane city limits, and working-from-home flexibility has broadened the buyer pool beyond traditional rail commuters to include buyers who value the lifestyle independently of the commute calculation.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

